  Game information:
  =================

  You and your friends are the  deadliest  killers  in  the  galaxy.  Another
  glorious day in the Corps.

  Buckle up,  soldier!  Welcome  to  Aliens:  Colonial  Marines.  Created  by
  Gearbox,  the  critically  acclaimed  and   fan-favourite   developers   of
  Borderlands and Brothers In Arms, you and your friends will become the most
  badass military outfit in the galaxy - the US Colonial Marines. It's up  to
  you  to  not  just  survive,   but   wipe   out   the   Xeno   infestation.
